social_posts.post_text: Went for another hike ! On film
Dad meditating ! Stoked to have a photo like this to hold onto. Dads 73 still going strong
Vintage trucks make everything look good
Crossing over to the interior world ! If you know of anyone looking to re design a space. Don’t be bashful

This last year has been quite awesome ! So many things have happened and I failed to document/share , road trips with Gwen, friends giving birth. Bowling nights with the family. Football and chili Sundays. repainting our home a jillion times. Men’s league basketball. Every goodwill in New England. Puzzles. We have put 40k miles on our car for a sense of how much travel was involved. We have developed a community in the Berkshires and have the luxury to work together in places all over the world. Looking forward to more fun, more friendships evolving. Hope y’all enjoy looking at all of our adventures
